---
import Avatar from "./icons/Avatar.astro"
---
<section id="why-trust-us" class="py-20 px-6 bg-base-100 border-t border-base-300 text-base-content">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">The Better Way to Replace Your Water Heater</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto opacity-90">
            We’re a licensed, family-run local team—not a franchise. We’ve eliminated the salesman to give you a faster, more honest experience.
        </p>
        <div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 text-left">
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-xl mb-2">Guaranteed Pricing</h3>
                <p>The price you see online is the price you pay. No salesmen, no commissions, and absolutely no surprise fees.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-xl mb-2">Licensed & Local</h3>
                <p>We handle the permits and bring everything to code. No subcontractors—just our local team doing work the right way.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-xl mb-2">Top-Tier Quality</h3>
                <p>We install professional-grade Rheem and Bradford White units backed by our <span class="font-semibold text-secondary text-nowrap">2-Year Labor Warranty</span>.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-primary text-xl mb-2">Respectful Service</h3>
                <p>We show up on time, protect your floors, and leave your home spotless. Most installs are finished same-day or next-day and in just a few hours.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
